title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 69-4.14 - Reporting
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 69-4.14 - Reporting

State Regulations
(a) Early intervention officials shall report to the department of Health such data as the department may require. (b) Approved early intervention evaluators, service providers, and service coordinators will provide to early intervention officials all the data necessary to complete required reports in a timely manner.
